Bletchley Installation Guide
============================

Dependencies
------------
* Python 2.7+ (3.x not yet well tested, but supported)
* scons (available as a package in most Linux distributions)
* gcc


Installing
----------
Build with:
 $ scons

And as root, install with:
 # scons install


Support
-------
Having trouble?  Submit an issue here: 
  http://code.google.com/p/bletchley/issues/list
